## 2. CSS / Tailwind

- **Entry:** `src/styles/index.css` imports `fonts.css`, `tailwind.css`, `theme.css`. All are used.
- **Tailwind:** Classes are generated from source; no separate “unused Tailwind file” list. Unused **utility usage** would require a Tailwind purge/scan; not done here.
- **No unused CSS files** identified; all style entry files are referenced.

- **`server/sessionInactivity.example.js`** – Example only; not run by this repo (no Node server in main app).
- **`server/sessionSystem.js`** – Backend session logic example.
- **`server/sessionIntegration.example.js`** – Integration example.

These are **reference/example** files. Safe to keep or remove depending on whether you use a Node backend elsewhere.

## 7. Cleanup script

From project root:

```bash
# List what would be deleted (no changes)
node scripts/cleanup-unused.js --dry-run

# Delete only the safe set (3 files: useInactivityLogout, PromoBanners, ProtectedRoute)
node scripts/cleanup-unused.js --safe

# Delete all reported unused (safe + optional + UI + imports). Run --dry-run first.
node scripts/cleanup-unused.js --all
```

**Recommendation:** Run `--dry-run` and `--safe` first; then run `--all` only if you are sure you do not need the UI/imports for future use.
